{"tid":349771,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[Poly]理大同學仔報咩OCAMP都好就千祈唔好報大O","createTime":"2017-08-06T18:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T15:05:37.000Z","uid":133996,"like":54,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b320195c941a6fbe5dc506915082a0c8cd0ae3cf","tid":349771,"uid":133996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:21:57.000Z","msg":"先歡迎一眾理大新生！黎緊8月12-14會係報ocamp既日子(oday)<br />\n前幾年會有個大O booth <br />\n(大O = 學生會搞 中O = 學院faculty 搞 細o =學系 Department搞)<br />\n今年係冇大O架 大家如果行過有人叫你報名,千祈千祈唔好比錢<br />\n因為今年冇學生會,所以唔應該會有大O,如果去左既話保險唔包,學校唔認可,早幾年仲因為玩OCAMP死過人（暗O）<br />\n大家入到大學都想開開心心玩姐,記住記住唔好報大O呀!!!"},{"pid":"52bb0d804446ee7b65697f9a9b98164d93a208f9","tid":349771,"uid":133996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家要小心呀 咪撚中伏"},{"pid":"56d26f2a3938f2a43443d60cc9046613cbf21385","tid":349771,"uid":34710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:34:52.000Z","msg":"而家係咪可能無大O<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8457ea64707a88690fc9df0e4d247cc70cbcb35","tid":349771,"uid":29473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:39:46.000Z","msg":"講起暗o poly班友真係老手<br />\n<a href=\"http://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/155857925-main-camp-唔退錢-冇保險%E3%80%80直擊-理大暗o-犯禁招\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftvb4life.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F155857925-main-camp-%E5%94%94%E9%80%80%E9%8C%A2-%E5%86%87%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%25E3%2580%2580%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%97o-%E7%8A%AF%E7%A6%81%E6%8B%9B&d=nNcQ2isqBi7IpGb3N8dlbnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=603308bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/155857925-main-camp-唔退錢-冇保險%E3%80%80直擊-理大暗o-犯禁招</a>"},{"pid":"2cecb095a63c9f92922538e5f217bc094f7614eb","tid":349771,"uid":133996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score